Earning Your Freedom	KEY:Earning Your Freedom~ Trait	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.CampaignTrait	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Earning Your Freedom~ Trait],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.CampaignTrait]		DESC:You've been a slave your whole life, and have passed from master to master more times than you can count. Some of those masters were cruel, others kindly. In all cases, you've yearned to be free.																					MULT:YES	CHOOSE:NUMCHOICES=1|STRING|Fortitude|Reflex|Will														BONUS:CHECKS|%LIST|1|TYPE=Trait								SOURCEPAGE:p.9
