Missionary			KEY:Missionary ~ Trait			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.CampaignTrait	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Missionary ~ Trait],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.CampaignTrait]			DESC:You've spent much of the last several years serving your faith, and the conviction and dedication to your church has impressed many.																																		CHOOSE:NUMCHOICES=1|SKILLSNAMED|Bluff|Diplomacy|Intimidate|Knowledge (Religion)|TYPE=Perform|Sense Motive											BONUS:SKILL|LIST|1|TYPE=Trait	CSKILL:LIST	SOURCEPAGE:p.10
